settings.text:
When you think of swimwear, you likely don’t think about high necklines. After all, most styles are swooping
so low in the front that they’re absolutely impossible to wear if you have a large bust. But don’t be mistaken – high neckline bikini tops
are all the rage right now, and they’re super chic!
Making this the perfect beach to street look with some denim cut-offs!

Where many swim lines have their place in the sun, Kalles
transcends beach and the pool. The pieces transition seamlessly
as day or evening Ready-to-Wear, providing an innate versatility
your already established wardrobe.
One-piece swimsuits are hotter than ever, offering styles that are even sexier than itsy bitsy bikinis!
